column2: Insight Select Income Fund, formerly Cutwater Select Income Fund, is a diversified, closed-end, management investment company. The primary objective of the Fund is to maintain a high level of income. The Fund invests in corporate debt securities, asset backed securities, commercial mortgage-backed securities, residential mortgage-backed securities, municipal bonds, the United States treasury securities, common stock, preferred stock, and other assets and liabilities. The Fund's investment portfolio includes automotive, chemicals, diversified financial services, energy, food and beverage, healthcare, industrial, insurance, media, mining, paper, real estate investment trust, retail and restaurant, technology, telecommunications, transportation and utilities. The Fund's investment advisor is Cutwater Investor Services Corp.
